  (hereinafter referred to as “the Guarantor/s” which expression shall, unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include his heirs, executors, legal representatives, administrators, attorneys) in favour of M/s. Samunnati Financial Intermediation & Services Pvt. Ltd., a Non-banking Financial Company incorporated under section 45 IA the Companies Act, 1934, registered with the Reserve Bank of India and having its registered office at Baid Hitech park , 129 b , 8th floor, SH 49, next to RTO office, Thiruvanmiyur, Chennai, Tamil Nadu 600041. India (hereinafter referred to as “the NBFC” which expression shall, unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include its successors and assigns); 
